312
00:25:31.863 --> 00:25:33.114
STAR CONSTRUCTION, MARCH INVOICE
MULA MARSO 1-31ST, 1987

313
00:25:58.181 --> 00:26:01.893
Ilang beses mo nang nakita ang ulo
