basa pa rin sa likod ng tenga.

392
00:31:06.531 --> 00:31:07.448
Damn it.

393
00:31:08.032 --> 00:31:10.952
Maaari ka bang maging walang pakialam tungkol dito?

394
00:31:11.035 --> 00:31:13.872
Freaking out tungkol dito
